      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kan010.wav",
      "text": "お、この間のライブバトルの記事出てる",
      "startTime": 12.36668879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "『元BIG4のⅢX対実力派のやさぐれポメラニアン』",
      "startTime": 16.6000221233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kan011.wav",
      "text": "『アイドルファンも唸る対戦カードだが、結果は』……",
      "startTime": 22.9000270904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kor009.wav",
      "text": "ふんふん……ふふん、私達のことべた褒めじゃない",
      "startTime": 28.06668879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うわ。にやにや笑っちゃってさ、キモっ。kanaは",
      "startTime": 34.9000251751,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kan012.wav",
      "text": "まだ『元BIG4』呼ばわりされてんのに腹立つけどな",
      "startTime": 39.3666968088,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "貴方、ライブバトルで一回勝って、褒められただけで",
      "startTime": 44.7666918418,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk013.wav",
      "text": "満足してるの？",
      "startTime": 48.5333634755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kor010.wav",
      "text": "……はっ。まさか",
      "startTime": 50.1000251751,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "腑抜けてはいないようで何よりよ",
      "startTime": 52.3333585085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk014.wav",
      "text": "――私達の目的はただ一つ、トップに立つことだけ",
      "startTime": 55.5333634755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "まだまだ倒さないといけない奴らはいるんだからね",
      "startTime": 60.0666918418,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kan013.wav",
      "text": "一度勝ったくらいで、浮かれてなんかいられないっつの",
      "startTime": 63.8000301422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "残りのBIG4、それに……",
      "startTime": 67.6333585085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk015.wav",
      "text": "月スト、サニピ、トリエル、リズノワ",
      "startTime": 70.7666968088,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "考えなければ",
      "startTime": 74.8333585085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-mhk016.wav",
      "text": "あの子達を倒すために、私達には何が必要なのか",
      "startTime": 77.0333634755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それじゃ、また会議といきましょうか？",
      "startTime": 81.8000251751,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2408_01_05-kor011.wav",
      "text": "観てる奴全員、驚かせてやろうじゃないの",
      "startTime": 85.7000301422,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}